articles.title: UEFA release short sharp statement on Tottenham vs Rennes match but are working to reschedule - Football.London
articles.description: European football's governing body have had their say on the Europa Conference League match that was meant to be taking place on Thursday evening
articles.content:
UEFA have confirmed that the Europa Conference League match between Tottenham Hotspur and Rennes is off and told football.london that they are working with both sides to try to reschedule the tie.
